* http://android.appstorm.net/roundups/lifestyle-roundups/top-10-minimal-and-elegant-android-news-reader-apps/:
    Take Home Notes for Developers:

    So what are the 10 best things you can do to improve your nest news based app?

        Go for minimal and elegant user interface
        Provide options for offline reading
        Dark and Light Themes
        Auto update on Wi-Fi only for 3G data conscious users
        Easy to add and manage news source
        Social sharing options
        Support for multimedia content
        Typography (use nice fonts and lots of white space)
        Share options should also link to default Android share settings like email and sms
        Go slow on the ads and maximize screen real estate
